title: [Robes of Resistance]
description: A wide burgundy and black screen creates a partitioned dressing area along a velvet-padded wall, opposite a series of burnished steel hooks beneath a brass-framed sign.  Open drawers hang precariously out of an oak cabinet, with hints of disarranged silks peeking from within.  Shoved within a corner is a pile of discarded shoes with torn vamps and broken soles.
